    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 8. Habitus. 1, Discheramocephalus bisulcatus; 2, D. vasilii; 3, Cissidium banari ♀; 4, C. banari ♂; 5, Dacrysoma ranomafanense; 6, D. varium; 7, D. denticulatum; 8, D. fusum." ;
