    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.247946>
    dc:description "FIGURES 41 – 55. Dacrysoma spp. antennomeres 3 – 11 (hairs omitted). 41, D. ranomafanense; 42, D. varium; 43, D. denticulatum; 44, D. ravelosoni; 45, D. rahanitriniainae; 46, D. dolorosum; 47, D. nigerrimum; 48, D. fabrum; 49, D. imitatum; 50, D. longulum; 51, D. subinsulsum; 52, D. andasibense; 53, D. fusum; 54, D. pilosum; 55, D. delicatum." ;
